  EffectDiscription_ENG: While you have a Digimon with [Dex] or [DeathX] in its name
    in play, you may use this card without meeting its color requirements. [Main]
    Delete 1 Digimon without [X Antibody] in its traits. If there are 3 or more Digimon
    in play, delete all Digimon without [X Antibody] in their traits instead.
